HEADWORD: Yellowing
<hw>Yel"low*ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act or process of making
yellow.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Softened . . . by the <qex>yellowing</qex> which time has
given.</q> <rj><qau>G. Eliot.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Yellowish</ent>⟦br⟧
